{
  "texts": [
    "Proprietary models typically show just a summary as their final output.",
    "For a detailed description, see Section 2.1 of Korinek (2024).To unlock the highest level of reasoning capabilities in the leading chatbots, user typically need a paid subscription from one of the leading model providers.",
    "Gemini 2.5 Pro and ChatGPT-5 automatically default to \"slow thinking\" mode when complex analytic questions are entered.",
    "In Claude, users can activate the setting \"Extended thinking\" to achieve the highest possible reasoning performance.",
    "The architecture of reasoning models allows them to excel at tasks that have consistently challenged traditional LLMs."
